      "rdfs:comment": "Nov 26–Dec 18, 2024 — superseding indictment Count 5 conduct on noneya5217_0am precedes Count 4 second-handle distribution beginning Dec 19; Dec 31, 2024 Count 6 defendant knowingly received child pornography via noneya66_lpk — accumulating material on Kik before Jan 7–Feb 2 proliferation of accounts noneya0502_bbf, noneyal307_bql, noneya3076_sm2",
